      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOULIN MISS (9) is in the premier stable and brings strong metro form to resumption. Proven fresh and owns an easy Doomben trial win. Has a handy 2kg claim and will be tough to beat. STATE IN TEXAS (1) peaks off three wins over 800m at Ipswich. He's run some decent races over 1000m, and Newman's 2kg claim is handy. Has a chance if things work out. HIDDEN MELODY (4) resumed here in Open grade and needed the outing. Proven second-up, and this suits much better. Has a 2kg claim and soft gate and has to be considered. CONCESSION (8) has been briefly freshened and was around the mark last time at Eagle Farm. Tumbles in weight and should enjoy a good run. FLAMING CONQUEST (3) peaks and may control the race from the inside gate. Is back from Open grade with a 2kg claim and will give a sight.",
